snippet.title: UFC Personal Trainer: Ultimate Fitness System Trailer (PS3, Xbox 360, Wii)
snippet.description:
Check out a two-minute trailer featuring the integration of UFC Personal Trainer with NASM, the National Academy of Sports Medicine.

For more on this game, check out: http://www.gamespot.com/6321047
